	<font color="#0d014d" style="font-family:arial;font-size:10pt;">
	Sony Online Entertainment is proud to announce the 2003 Spring Fan Faire in Las Vegas, Nevada! It will be held at the <a href="http://www.parkplace.com/hilton/lasvegas/" target="_blank">Las Vegas Hilton</a> on March 28th - 30th. Be sure to invite your guild mates, as there will be recognition for the guild with the highest attendance!<br><br>

And what’s an EverQuest Fan Faire without phat lewt? The Station Store, the ultimate purveyor of phat lewt, has always been an indispensable part of every Fan Faire and the Vegas event will be no exception. However, if you can’t wait till March 28th, you can get prepped for that wild and wacky Live Quest by visiting the <a href="https://store.station.sony.com/game_index.jsp?gamecode=EQ" target="_blank">Store</a> today and stocking up on EQ clothing, backpacks, watches, and other nifty items. <br><br>
<a href="http://everquest.station.sony.com/fanfaire/" target="_blank">Everquest FanFaire</a>
	<br><br>
	Posted By sobe	</td>
